title: Week 9 Waivers + Hockenson Trade, FAAB Dumps - Fantasy Football Podcast for 11/1
description:
Week 9 Waiver Wire! On today’s fantasy football podcast, the top waiver pickups at each position and reactions to T.J. Hockenson being traded to the Vikings! Plus, players to consider dropping, QB Streamers, and a recap of Monday Night Football. Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. Fantasy Football Podcast for November 1st, 2022.
